  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.26666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1800\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lRIrvTGkm9uyafnUK5KgPefLkhIrE4IicGHJHQeAMuKTMApustxsysABxO2U2Apm8SbM8WxNRADzicYEgdgCK58JLR8RxsM3duYgDc5Nrqd0c/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"244\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"154\" data-imgfileid=\"100009985\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260402125004_7306ef6.png\" style=\"font-size: 1rem; text-align: center; width: 100%;\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span data-eleid=\"3\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent时代，模型能力由模型智能以及其处理的context容量两个维度定义。一个能够原生处理图片、视频、文本等多模态context，同时擅长复杂编程、</span><span data-eleid=\"3\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-eleid&quot;:&quot;3&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">长程规划、</span></span><span leaf=\"\">动作执行的Codin</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">g基座模型，将是所有AI原生应用的基石。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">今天，我们发布<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">GLM-5V-Turbo</span>，</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">面向视觉编程打</span><span leaf=\"\">造的多模态Coding基座</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">模型。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">GLM-5V-Turbo从预训练阶段深度融合视觉与文本能力，让编程不再局限于纯文本输入。模型能看懂设计稿、截图、</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">网页界面，并据此生成完整可运行的代码，真正做到看得懂画面、写得出代码。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <div></div>\n  <p></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">核心要点如下：</span></span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:20px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">原生多模态Coding基座</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">：原生理解图片、视频、设计稿、文档版面等多模态输入，并支持画框、截图、读网页等多模态工具调用，上下文窗口扩展</span><span leaf=\"\">至200k，将Ag</span><span leaf=\"\">ent的感知-行动链路从纯文本延伸到视觉交互。</span></span></li>\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">兼顾视觉与编程能力</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">：在多模态Coding、Tool Use、GUI Agent等核心基准上取得领先表现。通过多任务协同RL等技术手段，确保纯文本场景下的编程、推理、工具调用等能力不退化。</span></span></span></li>\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">深度适配Claude Code与龙虾场景</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">：与Claude Code、OpenClaw/AutoClaw等Agent深度协同，支持“看懂环境→规划动作→执行任务”的完整闭环，并提供全套官方Skills，开箱即用。</span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 22px;padding-bottom: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">多模态Coding基座</span></span></h2>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">在多模态Coding、Agentic任务以及纯文本Coding维度的评测基准上，GLM-5V-Turbo</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">均以更小尺寸取得了领先表现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mnfh6l5s17lr\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6913155631986242\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2326\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 6px;background-color: transparent;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;width: 100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/lRIrvTGkm9uGFlEnhXlTJtibpBSNC9g9KriagbgGJVrpfqx6HqjmB0fEOXeQRlnia5qrPibxgkDz65jALKLaSfL8jS0aHhibh3LTeyWV6fM6qTN8/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"576\" data-cropsely2=\"398\" data-imgfileid=\"100009993\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260402125004_9a33c1a.png\"></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">GLM-5V-Turbo在设计稿还原、视觉代码生成、多模态检索与问答、视觉探查等基准上均取得领先表现；在衡量真实GUI环境操控能力的AndroidWorld、WebVoyager等基准上同样表现突出。</span><span data-pm-slice=\"2 2 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\">在纯文本Coding能力方面，GLM-5V-Turbo在CC-Bench-V2的</span><span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">Backend、Frontend和Repo Exploration</span></span><span leaf=\"\">三项核心基准测试中均保持稳定表现，表明<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">视觉能力引入后，纯文本编程与推理能力保持了同等水准</span>。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mnfh6sate58\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.35320754716981134\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2650\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 6px;background-color: transparent;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;width: 100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/lRIrvTGkm9sXdCBBrRNNZNNrBJrxXv23YhE9DHMhqrBk3NV0xykW0n2buL9YVPXukdy8a9rA1oRjohGSn9hrhIjBRZhfiaN5S1kmPmcDlZ3c/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"576\" data-cropsely2=\"203\" data-imgfileid=\"100009990\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260402125004_003120a.png\"></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">在AutoClaw等龙虾Agent中接入GLM-5V-Turbo后，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">龙虾具备了真正的视觉能力，能看懂屏幕上的信息</span>。模型在衡量龙虾Agent任务执行质量的PinchBench、ClawEval和ZClawBench上取得优异成绩，验证了其在复杂任务执行场景中</span></span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">的综合能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">内测阶段，字节跳动、美团、快手等互联网大厂<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">合作伙伴对GLM-5V-Turbo给予了高度评价</span>：</span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mng6i7mi1c7e\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">“GLM-5V-Turbo实现了从设计稿到代码的完整还原，作为一款视觉理解模型，能够很好地满足开发者的前端开发场景。”——TRAE模型测评团队</span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mng6i7mi1b3q\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">“原生多模态能力的引入并未削弱其编程逻辑，其编程能力仍属于国内第一梯队。增强了AI at Work领域下D2C、图片处理等方向的工作体验。”——美团某团队</span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mng6i7mi292\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">“它为Agent安上了「眼睛」，同时在编程领域展现出优于同类多模态模型的能力，在视觉编程场景中更具竞争力。”——快手万擎模型测评团队</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">-5V-Turbo能够取得性能领先在于其</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">模型架构、训练方法、数据构造、工具链四个层面的系统性升级</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">：</span></span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:20px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">原生多模态融合</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">：</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">GLM-5V-Turbo从预训练阶段开始进行文本与视觉能力深度融合，并在后训练阶段实现多模态协同优化。我们研发了新一代CogViT视觉编码器，在通用物体识别、细粒度理解、几何与空间感知上均达最优，也设计了兼容多模态输入且推理友好的MTP结构，在多模态场景下实现了较高的推理效率。</span></span></li>\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">30+ 任务协同强化学习</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">：</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">在强化学习阶段同时优化30+任务类型，覆盖STEM、grounding、video、GUI Agent等子领域，模型在感知、推理、Agentic执行和人类体感上均获稳健提升，协同强化学习有效缓解了单领域训练的不稳定性。</span></span></li>\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">Agentic数据与任务构造</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">：</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">针对Agent数据稀缺和验证困难的行业挑战，我们构建从元素感知到序列级动作预测的多层级体系，基于合成环境大规模生成可控、可验证的训练数据，并从预训练阶段即注入Agentic元能力（如将GUI Agent PRM数据加入预训练以降低幻觉），同时探索非对称优化，用多模态评估任务撬动更强的Agent能力。</span></span></li>\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">多模态工具链扩展</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">：</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">在文本工具基础上，GLM-5V-Turbo新增支持多模态搜索、画框、截图、读网页等多模态tools，将编程与任务执行的感知-行动链路从纯文本扩展到视觉交互。与Claude Code、AutoClaw等龙虾的协同效果进一步增强，支持“看懂环境→规划动作→执行任务”的完整闭环。</span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 22px;padding-bottom: 12px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">典型场景展示</span></span></h2>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">1.图像即代码</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">GLM-5V-Turbo尤其擅长核心视觉编程场景。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:20px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">前端复刻</span>：发送草图、设计稿、参考网站的截图或录屏，模型就能直接理解布局、配色、组件层级与交互逻辑，生成完整可运行的前端工程，准确还原版式、配色、动效等视觉细节。</span></span></li>\n   <li><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">GUI自主探索复刻</span>：结合Claude Code等框架，GLM-5V-Turbo能凭借自身强大的GUI Agent能力自主探索目标网站，浏览页面结构、梳理各页面之间的跳转关系、采集视觉素材与交互细节，最后基于记录的探索结果直接生成代码复现整个站点，实现从“看图复刻”到“GUI探索复刻”的能力跃升。</span></span></li>\n   <li><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">交互式编辑</span>：支持按需求增删页面模块、修改文案与样式、调整布局结构，并可补充按钮反馈、弹窗切换、表单联动等交互功能，实现可视化迭代编辑。</span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">2.为龙虾安上眼睛</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">龙虾的任务边界被大幅拓宽</span>，例如可以浏览网页和文档，生成图文并茂的报告、PPT，还可以查询并解读K线图等复杂图表。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">AutoClaw已上线“股票分析师”Skill，利用GLM-5V-Turbo的原生视觉能力，龙虾能直接看懂K线走势、估值区间图和券商研报图表，实现四路数据源60秒并行采集，输出</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">图文交错</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">的研报。立即在AutoClaw中</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">切换至GLM-5V-Turbo</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">，试试提问“帮我分析今天XXX的股价，生成专业分析报告”。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">除视觉编程与龙虾任务外，GLM-5V-Turbo在多模态搜索、深度研究、GUI Agent、感知Grounding等更广泛的Agentic场景中也实现了显著的</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">性能</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">提升。为此，我们提供了一组</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">官方Skills</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">，涵盖图像Captioning、视觉Grounding、基于文档的写作、简历筛选、提示词生成等原生能力，以及基于GLM-OCR和GLM-Image构建的文字识别、表格识别、手写体识别、公式识别和文生图能力，帮助用户在更多场景中释放模型的多模态潜力。上述Skills已上线ClawHub，一键安装即可体验全部能力。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:20px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">ClawHub链接</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">：<a href=\"https://clawhub.ai/zai-org/glm-master-skill\" target=\"_blank\">https://clawhub.ai/zai-org/glm-master-skill</a></span></span></span></li>\n   <li><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">GitHub链接</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">: &nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/zai-org/GLM-skills\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/zai-org/GLM-skills</a></span></span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 22px;padding-bottom: 12px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">立即体验</span></span></h2>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">欢迎广大用户通过以下方式接入GLM-5V-Turbo：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">1.产品体验</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:20px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">AutoClaw（澳龙）</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">：</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://autoglm.zhipuai.cn/autoclaw/\" target=\"_blank\">https://autoglm.zhipuai.cn/autoclaw/</a></span></span></li>\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">Z.ai</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">：</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://chat.z.ai\" target=\"_blank\">https://chat.z.ai</a></span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">2.官方API接入</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:20px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">BigModel 开放平台</span>：</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/guide/models/vlm/glm-5v-turbo\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/guide/models/vlm/glm-5v-turbo</a></span></span></li>\n   <li><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">Z.ai</span>：</span></span>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://docs.z.ai/guides/vlm/glm-5v-turbo\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.z.ai/guides/vlm/glm-5v-turbo</a></span></p></li>\n   <li><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">Coding Plan</span>：现面向Coding Plan用户开放申请；后续GLM Coding Plan也会纳入GLM-5V-Turbo，敬请期待。</span></span></li>\n   <ul style=\"padding-left:24px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;margin-top:0px;line-height:30px;margin-bottom:10px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">申请问卷：</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://zhipu-ai.feishu.cn/share/base/form/shrcndgpmRlJoD5rMmIavUrPwzg\" target=\"_blank\">https://zhipu-ai.feishu.cn/share/base/form/shrcndgpmRlJoD5rMmIavUrPwzg</a></span></span></li>\n   </ul>\n  </ul>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "智谱发布 GLM-5V-Turbo 多模态 Coding 基座模型，支持原生视觉理解与代码生成，深度适配 Agent 场景并提供 200k 上下文窗口。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "智谱发布 GLM-5V-Turbo 多模态 Coding 基座模型，支持原生视觉理解与代码生成，深度适配 Agent 场景并提供 200k 上下文窗口。",
  "summary": "智谱 AI 正式发布 GLM-5V-Turbo，这是一款专为视觉编程设计的多模态 Coding 基座模型。该模型在预训练阶段实现了视觉与文本的深度融合，能够直接理解设计稿、截图及网页界面并生成可运行代码。核心特性包括 200k 上下文窗口、原生多模态工具调用（如画框、截图）、以及针对 Agent 场景的深度优化。通过 30 多项任务的协同强化学习，模型在保持顶尖编程能力的同时，显著提升了 GUI Agent 的感知与执行闭环能力，并已深度适配 Claude Code 和 AutoClaw 等主流 Agent 框架。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "原生多模态融合打破了纯文本编程的局限。",
      "explanation": "模型从预训练阶段深度整合视觉与文本能力，使其能直接「看懂」设计稿和 UI 截图并转化为代码，实现从设计到代码（D2C）的直接跨越。"
    },
    {
      "point": "针对 Agent 场景构建了完整的感知-行动链路。",
      "explanation": "支持画框、截图、读网页等视觉工具调用，配合 200k 长上下文，使模型能胜任复杂的 GUI 自动化任务，实现「看懂环境→规划动作→执行任务」的闭环。"
    },
    {
      "point": "采用 30+ 任务协同强化学习确保能力不退化。",
      "explanation": "在引入视觉能力的同时，通过多任务优化确保了纯文本编程、逻辑推理等核心能力的稳健，在小尺寸模型上取得了领先的性能表现。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
